- restart channel or encoder async.

v-0.2.1 2013-2-25 zhangping
- pure pull mode encoder app src.
- FIN -> EPOLLIN bug fix.
- specify conf file in command line.
- seperate mgmt and streaming http port.
- kill itvencoder via http mgmt.

v-0.1.3 2012-12-20 zhangping
- bugfix.
- rpmbuild.
- autoconf and automake.
- gracefully close socket.
- daemonize.

v-0.1.2 2012-12-5 zhangping
- log to file, /var/log/itvencoder.log, and use logrotate.
- writev more data every time, avoid vlc exit.
- time output format, more readable.
- use events mutex, for crash bug.
- auto restart source pipeline or encoder pipeline.
- restart source and encoder pipeline via http interface.
- report request current status.
- access times.

v-0.1.1 2012-11-16 zhangping
- native http server.
- video deinterlace.
- channel monitor.
- get caps of decoder pipeline appsink and set caps of encoder pipeline appsrc.
